Deborah Owusu-Bonsu (a mụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 25 n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1984) nke a maara nke ọma site na aha ya dị ka Sister Derby bụ onye na-eme ihe ngosi telivishọn nke Ghana, onye egwu na onye nlereanya nke Akan na onye na-eme ihe ngosi na e.tv Ghana.
A mụrụ Deborah Vanessa Owusu-Bonsu na 25 Ọgọstụ 1984, nna Ashanti na nne ya bụ onye Romania
Nne na nna ya abụọ bụ ndị na-anakọta egwu ụwa na nka

Ọ bụ onye na-eme ihe ngosi televishọn, onye nlereanya, onye egwu, onye agụmakwụkwọ na onye na-ese ihe osise. Owusu-Bonsu bụ nwanne nwanyị nke onye egwu hip a ma ama bụ Wanlov the Kubolor onye pụtara na ihe nkiri Coz Ov Moni Owusu-Bonsu gara Kraist the King International School, mgbe ahụ Wesley Girls 'High School. Owusu-Bonsu gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Bachelor's Degree na Publishing Studies na Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology sochiri Master Degree na Book / Journal Publishing na University of the Arts London.

Owusu-Bonsu egosila ọkachamara ya na mmasị ya maka ubi ọ họọrọ site n'ịrụ ọrụ nke ọma maka obere ụlọ ọrụ yana nnukwu ụlọ ọrụ na Ghana, United States na United Kingdom. N'afọ 2012, Owusu-Bonsu dekọrọ ma wepụta otu egwu (egwu) nke akpọrọ 'Uncle Obama' na-ezo aka na Barack Obama nke ụlọ ọrụ telivishọn United States CNN kpuchiri. Kemgbe afọ 2012, Owusu-Bonsu bụ onye na-ahụ maka mmemme The Late Nite Celebrity Show nke ụlọ ọrụ telivishọn e.tv Ghana na-agbasa. O mechakwara ga GHOne Television ebe ọ kwadoro ihe ngosi ya, Gliterrati maka obere oge tupu ọ nyefee Berla Mundi.
Ya na onye egwu Medikal na-akpa ruo afọ atọ, tupu ha agbawa na 2018.
